thread.title: Tarnisha Mills
thread.title_full: Paper Divas reviewed by Tarnisha Mills

author: Tarnisha Mills
title: Tarnisha Mills
text: I ordered baby shower invitations recently, delivery was fast and quality of product great. Would recommend. Was slightly disappointed however when I messaged an enquiry prior to purchase and still have had no response. Also the heading on the invite appeared to be glittery on the preview however once purchased and received it was not glittery, just the illusion of glitter texture. But overall great product.
